snippet.title: F3 2021 Trailer - Super Mario Craft - 1.17
snippet.description:
The edited Trailer for the F3 2021 presentation
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1DlhJbiMsW0

Super Mario Craft is the perfect fit for every Mario Fan! Experience the Minecraft World like it was a Nintendo Game. Fill your world with colorful, vibrant blocks and new cool and custom models for the minecraft creatures.



Super Mario Craft Discord:
https://discord.gg/MZcGhp953k

- Always the newest Verion (with Optifine)
- Custom entity models and conected textures
- Mario stiled custom textures
- Every item and block is changed

Now available on any Minecraft Java with Optifine. 

Download it on Minecraft CurseForge:
https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/super-mario-craft


Super Mario Master Mode Musik:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3BUnUZMH0Wo


#minecraft #Minecraftmods #supermario
